headline.main: Barb Moxness Leads Legends Tour's Walgreens Charity Classic.
headline.print_headline: Barb Moxness Leads Legends Tour's Walgreens Charity Classic.

lead_paragraph: Barb Moxness shot a 5-under 67 on Saturday to take a one-stroke lead after the first round of The Legends Tour's Walgreens Charity Classic.
